Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A devil came to this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first priority is to help Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wim?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl came asking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.63,0:00:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:00:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to the vampire's mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked exactly like the twins in the drawings there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The twins in the drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they call her Nina now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's called Nina now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.41,0:01:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always said people should cherish\Ntheir names, right, Mr. Poppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you seen my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've looked everywhere, but I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have something important to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right after that, let's go find your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad hasn't killed anyone, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father isn't that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, go hide in the general store over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Wim and find somewhere to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally meet, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's die...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's die together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:29.55,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(288,100)\pos(356,345)}The Landscape of the End
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find Franz Bonaparta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the Red Rose Mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he said to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget everything you saw just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run far away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, you see, people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can become anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are both beautiful jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can't become monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Poppe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Poppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Poppe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Run, Wim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The landscape of the end..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To you, all life was equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you should've realized it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing everyone is equal in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The landscape of the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not shoot, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we were the last two people in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I can do for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some things can't be taken back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma is going to shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A devil came to this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and slaughtered everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from my Wim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the D-KMIF!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've landed in the western side of Ruhenheim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've secured the eastern side of town, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attend to the townspeople immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there even any survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We of the DNN news crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:14:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have finally managed to make it into\Ntown by climbing a hill to the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This case is unprecedented!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that the town was nearly\Nwiped out in a mass slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WKat exactly happened in this quiet\Ntown in southern Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, we've only taken one\Nsuspect into custody so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Herbert Knaup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Age 38, unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's admitted to the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he shot at a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad shot him trying to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it appears he has an extremely\Nhigh blood alcohol level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason he said he committed the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was that a seven-headed monster\Nwith horns was attacking his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's spewing some nonsense here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got disconnected again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I explained exactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A young man named Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,annihilated this town so he could commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you explain it so that even\Nwe can understand, Dr. Gillen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be a long story...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I tell you everything, you\Nstill might not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've found an injured officer in the Versteck Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't think his life is in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's drifting in and out of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there even one officer who\Ncan explain this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:15:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Inspector Lunge of the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have my ID on me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try contacting the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the man who is essentially\Nresponsible for this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to finish him off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I left him and headed downstairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard his voice behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A moment later...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received a blow to the back of my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said something to me at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't see it yet."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The landscape of the end."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll get more details after you've been treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see some identification?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hennich. I live on Erft Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my wife, Franka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anything that can prove your identities?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the lottery ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I put it in my pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go look for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must've dropped it somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can live like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anything to prove your...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to show me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any other survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some identification...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check every single one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There may still be survivors in the buildings!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, with that head injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had the best neurosurgeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might you be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the fugitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Dr. Tenma, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lunge of the BKA is calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to tell you that there is\Na patient who needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad isn't a killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of things we want to ask your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was only trying to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you did back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what you're going to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad..!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad isn't a killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's begin the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:31.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,471)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.47,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:26.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:34.43,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:36.89,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
